OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly rain in the east clearing
OL,6,Fthis morning, although may linger for
OL,7,Fmuch of the day across northeast
OL,8,FScotland. Otherwise widespread showers
OL,9,Fdeveloping, with the showers heavy and
OL,10,Fthundery in places. Temperatures
OL,11,Faround average for early June.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing this evening,
OL,14,Fbut a few continuing overnight, mainly
OL,15,Facross the north and west. Clear
OL,16,Fspells developing for a time, but
OL,17,Ffurther rain reaching western parts by
OL,18,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
